@AdguardTeam/filters-maintainers if you have a test device with Android, then could you please take a look at this issue?
This app is marked as potentially unsafe by few antivirus vendors and by Chrome itself, so I don't want to install it.


There is a link to download app - `https://m.dongqiudi.com/guide`

